OL,5, A team of Amazon workers has forced the
OL,6, technology giant to recognise a trade  
OL,7, union in the US for the first time.    
OL,9,FWorkers at a New York warehouse voted  
OL,10,F55% in favour of joining the Amazon    
OL,11,FLabor Union.                           
OL,13,FThe group is led by former Amazon      
OL,14,Fworker Chris Smalls, who made his name 
OL,15,Fprotesting against safety conditions at
OL,16,Fthe retail giant during the pandemic.  
OL,18,FMr Smalls' victory marks a major defeat
OL,19,Ffor Amazon, which had fiercely fought  
OL,20,Fagainst unionisation.                  
